b_ul\"><li> 65 levels<br></li><li> 6 worlds, each with unique challenges<br></li><li> Original Soundtrack</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Usability Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Full Screen/Windowed mode<br></li><li> Resolution settings<br></li><li> Music and SFX control with seperate sliders<br></li><li> Rebindable hotkeys<br></li><li> Various 3D related settings<br></li><li> Unlimited undo<br></li><li> Unlimited level skipping<br></li><li> No timer</li></ul>Mouse and Keyboard is required to play this game.",
